'''Veritrade''' is a privately owned [[commercial intelligence]] company founded in 1999,<ref name="peru21">{{cite web|url=http://peru21.pe/noticia/699341/veritrade-mundo-comercial-gira-nuestras-manos|title=Veritrade: ‘El mundo comercial gira en nuestras manos’ – Perú 21|publisher=peru21.pe|accessdate=2014-04-19}}</ref> dedicated to providing information about [[International trade]] from multiple countries, in the form of [[Electronic publishing|digital publications]].

Through the use of its database,<ref name="database">[[Database]]</ref> Veritrade incorporates different products for varied sectors and industries in Peru and worldwide.

==Products==
Veritrade has developed several products that allow reading and analyzing data on foreign trade for each country, with different specifications catering to different types of industries, businesses and individual clients: Veritrade Business, Veritrade Analytic, Veritrade Motors and Verinews.

These products are based on the use of information technology<ref name="informationtechnology">[[Information technology]]</ref> and help clients to analize production, costs, etc.

==Collaboration with media==
Veritrade collaborates with different online and printed media outlets providing foreign trade data and analysis. The most notable examples are articles in newspapers El Comercio,<ref name="elcomercio">{{cite web|url=http://elcomercio.pe/gastronomia/409584/noticia-pisco-desplazo-al-aguardiente-chileno-estados-unidos_1|title=El pisco desplazó al aguardiente chileno en Estados Unidos &#124; El Comercio Perú|publisher=elcomercio.pe|accessdate=2014-04-19}}</ref> Perú21<ref name="Peru21">{{cite web|url=http://peru21.pe/noticia/502605/mis-finanzas-decalogo-exportacion|title=El Decálogo de la Exportación &#124;Perú21|publisher=peru21.pe|accessdate=2014-06-02}}</ref> and Gestión.<ref name="gestion">{{cite web|url=http://gestion.pe/noticia/628332/exportacion-cafe-crece-397-ultimos-10-anos|title=Gestión &#124; EL DIARIO DE ECONOMÍA Y NEGOCIOS DE PERÚ|author=gestion.pe|publisher=gestion.pe|accessdate=2014-04-19}}</ref>

In May 2014, Veritrade provided foreign trade information relevant to an ongoing murder investigation, featured in a local news coverage.<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l9SqO7e1EIM&feature=youtu.be&t=2m36s</ref>

